         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-02/3.jpg?VersionId=KJ.f74rZN4h8vg8uECT9OQXYq8lFdiQX&amp;itok=mtNX7BZL" alt="" data-caption="卫冕冠军羽生结弦在本届冬奥会比赛中最终排名第四，无缘奖牌。（新华社）" src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2022-02/3.jpg?VersionId=KJ.f74rZN4h8vg8uECT9OQXYq8lFdiQX&amp;itok=mtNX7BZL" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
